intent.user_query: Find products sold in the last week.

phases.goal: Execute SQL query on fitness_db: SELECT DISTINCT p.ProductID, p.ProductName FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON sd.SaleID = s.SaleID WHERE s.SaleDate >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '7' DAY;

arguments.sql: SELECT DISTINCT p.ProductID, p.ProductName FROM fitness_db.Products p JOIN fitness_db.SaleDetails sd ON p.ProductID = sd.ProductID JOIN fitness_db.Sales s ON sd.SaleID = s.SaleID WHERE s.SaleDate >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '7' DAY;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
